        <Parent_String>Vietnamese regional styles and periods [300019242], Vietnamese (culture or style) [300019239], Southeast Asian [300120146], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
